summary: Added comprehensive debugging to AutoCompleteSearch component to diagnose why suggestions are not appearing. Added console logs to track component state, API calls, and fallback to local suggestions. This will help identify whether the issue is with the API not being called, API returning empty results, or the component not displaying suggestions properly.
current_status: Debug logging added to AutoCompleteSearch component. The console will now show detailed information about the component state, API responses, and suggestion generation to help identify why the autocomplete suggestions are not working as expected.
